# 高德地图 (AMap) Web 端 JS API key — required to show the real basemap in the
# riding HUD. Without it the app falls back to a GPS "trace canvas".
#
# How to get one:
#   1. Register at https://lbs.amap.com (高德开放平台)
#   2. 控制台 → 应用管理 → 创建应用 → 添加 Key
#   3. 服务平台选「Web端 (JS API)」
#   4. Copy the key below into a local .env.local (which is gitignored)
#
# If your key requires a security code (安全密钥), set VITE_AMAP_SECURITY too.

VITE_AMAP_KEY=
VITE_AMAP_SECURITY=
